item.title: pre youth council
item.description: 8:22pm Friday 23 July 1999 In 12 hours I leave for 2 weeks in Iowa. I haven’t packed yet. The first week I’ll be an adult-at-large on Youth Council, and the second week I’ll be an advisor at Con Con. Each of these events are youth empowering, youth organized, youth everything, and I’m proud to be a part of the wonderfulness. I do not have a laptop yet (haven’t had the proper cashflow for one) so I may write a mega entry at the end of it all, but maybe will figure out a way to write while I’m there.
